* \\:-)	[[smileys/smile.png]]
* \\:D	[[smileys/biggrin.png]]
* \\:-D	[[smileys/biggrin.png]]
* \\B)	[[smileys/smile2.png]]
* \\B-)	[[smileys/smile2.png]]
* \\:))	[[smileys/smile3.png]]
* \\:-))	[[smileys/smile3.png]]
* \\;)	[[smileys/smile4.png]]
* \\;-)	[[smileys/smile4.png]]
* \\:\	[[smileys/ohwell.png]]
* \\:-\	[[smileys/ohwell.png]]
